Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.52,0:00:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is to all investigators!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.35,0:00:05.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move to the house of Nabei Eiki immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.52,0:00:08.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's highly likely that he is now in possession of Takagi's handgun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:12.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take absolute caution, there's little time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:16.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any minute could cost our man his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:24.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:27.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it, they must have...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Figured it all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:30.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:31.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:39.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just because of the hot springs promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} have to die for it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:50.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hot spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:52.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:00:53.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:55.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He happened to put this material evidence in his pocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, following the pattern, the criminal's bullet landed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:08.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since they finished the treatment, he's been in the ward...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:10.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sound asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:15.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love is eternal, labyrinths are mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:16.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saturday nights are for mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:19.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitou Kid's challenge notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:21.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His target this time is the world's strongest safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:23.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.97,0:01:25.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:27.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:17.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"A Life and Death Decision."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"A lone police officer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Was able to fight off a hail of gunfire and single-handedly\Narrest the suspect, we learned the following day."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:28.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The article about Detective Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, mostly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only reason it happened at all is because he was able to get my gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:36.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only reason anyone realized the scar was\Nactually on the serial murderer's back...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:43.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was due to my brilliant deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:46.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And once again, I don't remember a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was good to solve the case, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:50.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:53.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For a few reasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:02.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:03.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:04.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blushing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something good happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:10.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:12.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:14.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:19.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:22.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the ward, with Detective Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:27.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such optimism...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:31.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy just keeps on winning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:32.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Time after time, that arrogant thief has evaded capture...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He keeps defeating me every single time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:46.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:48.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it too hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:50.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:56.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On occasion, it's a perfect match for my cold heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your cold heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because there hasn't been any news from Kid lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:05.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't had the chance to compete with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:08.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the newspaper...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's being reported everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:20.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Kaitou Kid has sent a challenge notice\Nto his old rival Suzuki Jirokichi," it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:28.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Advisor Suzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:29.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, elaborate on the details!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:35.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is Kid coming to steal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Who knows"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The following was written on his notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:50.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"It came to me, Senior Advisor Suzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:54.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"That we should stop these senseless bouts of ours\Nand take on the compliant nature of a newborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"When darkness next consumes the moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Await me at the grand safe kept precious in your family home...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:02.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"And look forward to my surpassing it."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Signed, "Kaitou Kid."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The grand safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could he mean, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:09.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was constructed during the Tokugawa shogunate period by\Nthe master of traps, Samizu Kichiemon, just prior to his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:19.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the grand and impregnable safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:21.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Iron Tanuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:25.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the challenge notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:33.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While it seems that guy's interest has nothing to\Ndo with the contents but instead the safe itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:41.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Iron Tanuki's door has never failed to repel even the most famous\Nof thieves, and I'm sure it will gladly challenge the one to come next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:43.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for whether that guy can really get it open...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be a pleasure to witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To hell with this "pleasure" business!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:50.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You decided, even after receiving a notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:53.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That it was best to go to the press first instead of the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:54.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing pleasurable about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Inspector Nakamori from the Tokyo Metropolitan Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What measures are in place for repelling Kid this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori, please comment!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:03.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's there to say —\hI just heard about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:11.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I suggest you take a careful look at the challenge notice first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't his normal drawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:22.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I deemed it unnecessary to notify the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe it's merely an impostor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why the hell didn't you tell that to the press?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should I come out victorious and the world still believes it's authentic...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can add it to my memoirs of bravery, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:39.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can this old guy still be thinking about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, the aid of the police won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:45.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't actually Kaitou Kid, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:54.20,Signs,,0,0,0,,Three Days Later
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:53.91,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It could be a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:57.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The challenge notice sent by Kaitou Kid, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:08:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what Uncle Jirokichi has been saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did send it to you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A photo-copy of that notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:05.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something was off, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His symbol did seem different from how it usually is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:15.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, all of his notices have featured horizontal writing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, for the first time, this one was written vertically.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The composition itself also seemed dated...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:24.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why'd you bother calling us here as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A lady's intuition!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:30.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, I still have the feeling Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} will appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it seems I'm not the only one that feels that way, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:36.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:38.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down just because it might be an impostor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"When darkness next consumes the moon"\Nrefers to the next new moon, which is tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:46.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surround the safe room and secure it as tight as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:49.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:51.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course he's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:54.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what's the point in surrounding the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:58.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems more natural to position everyone just outside of the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:01.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would be pointless, Detective Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not come see my prized Iron Tanuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:10.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The safe of Samizu Kichiemon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, from back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:16.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kichiemon is the one who designed that mansion full of traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is that impenetrable vault, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:33.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just from looking, it seems you'd end up\Nbreaking a bone or two trying to pry it open.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:43.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no furniture in here at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But putting it in the wall makes it look\Nmore like an actual vault than a safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:49.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's four meters short of a six-tatami mat room in size.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The walls around it are covered in 50 centimeters of steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:03.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back during the war, when I was still just a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:08.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My parents and I would seek refuge inside to wait out the air-raids.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, that means there are holes for air, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:12.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:16.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a small gap for ventilation under the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:20.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The opening is only about three centimeters in all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, to get out, didn't someone have to open it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a simple matter to open it from the inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I may well be the only one still alive\Nthat knows how to open it from out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, how about we take a closer look?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:36.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:42.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe you're a smoker, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:45.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I borrow a cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:47.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, here's one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a bodyguard I employed a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:01.64,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Gotou Zengo (38)\NBodyguard
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:01.22,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Not much of a talker, but he's dependable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, if you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:19.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:20.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, just wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:30.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It became a complete prison just like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's all thanks to a weight sensor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even the weight of just one cigarette can set it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess that's why there's no furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:42.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surely you understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:45.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy won't even be able to get close to the safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:51.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This old guy sure is fond of enclosures...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:56.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akitsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:59.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get in there and dispose of that cigarette that's rolling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:05.32,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}Akitsu Masuhiko (32)\NAssistant
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:05.32,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,If i go in there now, I'll end up locked in the cage ass well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:06.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've switched it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now take this time to get in there and clean it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's another new one I hired a few days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he's proven to be mostly useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:22.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:23.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for this cigarette...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should I return it to Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:27.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would he smoke something that's been on the floor!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:32.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Throw that in the trash right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you're done with that, I'd appreciate\Nit if you'd move away from the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're getting in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:46.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I already tell you it was a waste of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is just a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:56.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Mouri, you may go now as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure nothing will happen tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:12:58.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:03.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, that includes this little guy\Nthat's regarded as his natural enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:06.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess it's time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:09.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, it doesn't look like Kid's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But can't you wait just a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:23.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:27.74,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I was looking for that doggy, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:29.16,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}Seto Mizuki (23)\NMaid
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:29.16,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I accidentally hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, do you mean the doggy of my uncle's?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:40.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle's dog, Lupin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, was looking ill earlier, so apparently\Nhe sent him off to the clinic—or so, that's what Uncle said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:43.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't know, even being the maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:47.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just came today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:50.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's really too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:53.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was looking forward to this, because I\Nheard there was a really cute doggy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, my own doggy passed away last month...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:02.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I had raised it since I was young, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was already growing pretty old.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:06.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm doing this during work hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:09.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:11.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:15.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent Chaki has issued a removal order.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:21.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems it was due to pressure from Advisor Suzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:27.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, the superintendent and that old guy were\Nalumni of the same university and got along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:34.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the safe is already outfitted with extraordinary security measures...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:38.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, even without our help, it should be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:46.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and turn off the anti-theft device!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something in the middle of the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like a card!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:55.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"As stated in the notice, I will appear before the\Nmoon's face greets us from beyond the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:03.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"And take that which lies in the stomach of the Iron Tanuki."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:06.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitou Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:08.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the real one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:11.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, how did the card get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't the sensor go off?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:20.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, let's find the reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police task force has surrounded the Suzuki residence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:41.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitou Kid's offensive is moments away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More and more members of the riot squad are joining the effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Given that Kid is up against such a massive police assembly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will he still appear as he claimed in his notice!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:54.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what, that guy will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:58.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll do something about that daring grin of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of you, take notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:05.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today is the day we catch that guy and\Nwipe that damn smirk off his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is some fuss you're making over a mere impostor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although the composition and mark on the first smelled of a fake...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:24.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was most likely meant to serve as a taunt to we police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:28.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the notice that showed up inside the room with the vault...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt that this was the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it strange for you to keep insisting that even this points to a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, even if that is the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:41.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This sort of excessive security force is unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:43.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.18,0:16:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy's target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:51.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The legendary and impregnable safe crafted by\Nthe trap master, Samizu Kichiemon, himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:54.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's out to open the door of the Iron Tanuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:17:02.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The multitude of mechanisms and gears in the door make it so\Nintricate that no thief will be able to force their way inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Given that I'm the only one who knows how to open it, anyone else\Nwho tries and fails may end up losing their life in the process...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you no one else can open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You need to keep in mind that we're dealing with\Nthe "Magician Under the Moonlight," Kaitou Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:19.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter what kind of safe it is, that\Nguy will be in there before you know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even should he have the ability to crack it, he can't even get near it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I show you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That defensive mechanism protecting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:30.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that guy takes even one step into the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weight sensor on the floor will ensure that he finds\Nhimself trapped in the iron prison, like a rat in a sack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:41.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hasn't Kid already gotten into the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he delivered this notice there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:51.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's obvious that he already has a way to bypass the security setup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:52.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Kaitou Kid put the notice there, he must\Nhave been one of the people near us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because when the door was first opened, there was nothing there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But after it was opened the next time, the notice was inside, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:11.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That whole time, we were near the room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If something were to be placed there while the weight sensor\Nwas disabled, wouldn't it pick it up when it was reactivated?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:26.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the design is such that it only registers\Nnew weight after it's switched back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:30.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means he could have placed it there while it was switched off...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:31.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle switched it off earlier, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:34.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:40.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To demonstrate how the weight sensor\Nworked, he threw the cigarette into the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:44.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:44.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:46.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, just wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:55.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He then turned off the switch to collect the cigarette.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:18:58.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akitsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get in there and dispose of that cigarette that's rolling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I go in there how, I'll end up locked up in the cage as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:10.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've switched it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now take this time to get in there and clean it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:13.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:16.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:19.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's another new one I hired a few days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:21.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he's proven to be mostly useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:30.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That assistant —he was the one who went in to get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:33.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means he could've been Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:37.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While feigning to get the cigarette, he might have put the notice there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:41.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I don't think that assistant is the\Nonly one who could have put it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:45.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bodyguard for Uncle Jirokichi could have, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:49.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he could have tossed it in while Uncle had the door open.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:53.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That maid that just came today could have done it as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:57.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was on her knees looking for the doggy, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:03.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, while the switch was off, the maid wasn't near the door, was she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The security device was demonstrated from this door, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the room housing the safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:16.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, another door leads to it over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:21.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Kid really were the maid, while he was searching for the dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:25.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could have slid the notice under the door\Nwhile the guards weren't watching, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:31.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle was talking in a really loud voice at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:33.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His voice may have carried over there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:35.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:39.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if we were on this side, she would know the switch was off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, these three were ones he just hired recently, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means the chances of Kid being in disguise are fairly high...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bring that Akitsu guy and the maid here immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:58.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll tug at his face and find out...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:21:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just who he's really disguised as!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:02.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means the first is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:06.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bodyguard{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}—your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:13.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I consider my staff part of my family from the day they're hired!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:17.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't permit the police to come and do what they please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:19.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:24.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're sure that it has to be Kid, make me believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:28.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, I'll be having a meal in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep the disturbances to a minimum out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:34.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'd know immediately if we could just have a pull at their faces...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:39.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something's different about Uncle today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.23,0:21:41.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, usually...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:45.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would be glaring and saying, "I need to see that\Nthief with my own eyes" with such excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:47.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:50.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's more like, "This has to be an impersonator."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:53.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even, "Make me believe that it's him."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:57.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} has come as Uncle this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:21:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something's definitely off...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:05.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Kid's notice arrived...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:07.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could have already been in the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:12.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But does that make it normal to hire three all-new employees at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.72,0:22:16.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, Kid's behavior from the first notice was strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if the dated writing on the first\Nnotice was meant to taunt the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What reason did he have for returning\Nto his usual style in the second one?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:31.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something behind this case...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.62,0:22:38.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.66,0:24:02.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he could be disguised as any of them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:05.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as the brat said earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.84,0:24:08.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's the bodyguard with the dark complexion, Gotou...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.26,0:24:11.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That mostly useless assistant, Akitsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.88,0:24:14.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the clumsy maid, Mizuki—that's all three.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.85,0:24:18.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this really be Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.35,0:24:22.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rest is on you, little guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.29,0:24:47.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.04,0:24:49.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suzuki Jirokichi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.92,0:24:51.51,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.55,0:24:52.97,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,But wasn't Uncle the hint?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.97,0:24:55.01,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hint{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}!
